"""
AppleIIBus_Edge — Apple II 50-pin peripheral-slot card edge (25 fingers x 2 sides, 0.1").

Full, canonical //e slot pinout on the symbol so this can be lifted into another project and
used as a REAL slot connector. Model-specific pins: 19 SYNC (slot-7 only), 35 COLORREF (=M2B0 on
IIgs), 39 USER1 (=65C02 SYNC / M2SEL on IIgs).

In THIS project the slot is MECHANICAL ONLY (single-star-point grounding is at the CPU socket),
so every finger is an optional pin left UNCONNECTED (floating gold). Footprint carries
exclude_from_bom / exclude_from_pos. Outline + footprint lifted from the prior AppleTini board.
"""

p1 = io(Net, optional=True)
p2 = io(Net, optional=True)
p3 = io(Net, optional=True)
